        "timestamp": 1736461499
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Thank you all!<br>\nI checked that addarith works, and it is good to know that linarith is the same as addarith.<br>\nrwa [add_comm] also works, and it is a good technique to keep in mind. Is there any good place to search for known lemmas like add_comm?</p>",
